snippet.textDisplay: I was an organic MUA and mostly formulate my own cosmetics... but the one thing I always thought was how lovely your products were.  On the most part they all look and appear to perform brilliantly.  Blood Sugar seems the siren for me, I have made no dupes for most of these shades and is the one palette I really wanted above anything else I saw released over the years.  After surgery yesterday my friend bought the palette for and I am getting today... I am so stoked and will use it a ton.  It's rare I buy branded makeup... but this is an amazing palette.  Can't wait to get it, good luck on your releases and the promo looks awesome x
